{"tid":800474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港咁多人煙民覺得做火車頭冇問題","createTime":"2018-08-31T01:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T02:49:06.000Z","uid":123613,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a612663346c071a26ee9b3ada24be33e42b5be42","tid":800474,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1524198517922509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1524198517922509&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=830ae845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1524198517922509</a><br />\n<br />\n大家覺唔覺成日做火車頭既人好黑人憎（邊行邊食煙既人），條街咁多人咁窄，後面既人全部要吸二手煙，就算條路闊，行動方便既人都可以跑快啲爬頭，但係行動不變既人呢？被迫要吸二手煙。（唔好拉埋咩汽車廢氣／唔好出街／唔好呼吸等無關痛癢既野，而家討論既係食煙，唔係其他話題）<br />\n<br />\n一出完個post個個煙民起晒鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1ca1398814102ee915dec058ce66304570e48e","tid":800474,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7475ce7c02d89e511548a7e273724a30da2ec73","tid":800474,"uid":48724,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12e73d8239cf4cdc3ae5d5e6626de181d3f8ae3a","tid":800474,"uid":202179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"渣支水槍仔出街，替天行道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48361dc1456c9933f5bd0294e35a8328cb37f00","tid":800474,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:02:10.000Z","msg":"煙民全部正垃圾<br />\n週地都係煙頭"},{"pid":"211b819a234b98c3e3010e